query:
INSERT INTO osm_highway_features (
                id,
                feature_type,
                properties,
                geometry,
                geometry_type,
                created_at
            ) VALUES (
                $1, 
                'Feature', 
                $2, 
                ST_GeomFromGeoJSON($3), 
                $4,
                $5
            )
            ON CONFLICT (id) DO UPDATE SET
                properties = EXCLUDED.properties,
                geometry = EXCLUDED.geometry,
                geometry_type = EXCLUDED.geometry_type
